summary: App enables you to easily access key information about your fleet or assets.
description: The pressure to keep up with your business doesn't stop when you're away from the computer. The MotoMon / Eurosat Mobile App enables you to easily access key information about your fleet or assets, anytime and anyplace. Receive alerts, investigate incidents, and if needed, send the nearest technician to an urgent job or react to assets in danger, all from your phone.Note: You must be a MotoMon or Auto-GPS customer to use this app. Not a MotoMon or Auto-GPS customer? Try out our free demo access and contact us at www.motomon.com or www.auto-gps.eu

comments: Best GPS tracking app Fast, easy & accurate!!!
Mobile Asset GPS Tracking This app has everything you'd want to be able to track your mobile assets. Very well designed and easy to use!

Does just what we need it to Use daily to locate driver for pick-up of work and this app does it quickly giving us just what we need. Love the  auto sign on feature and very few screens to get to pertinent info.
